org.safs.selenium.webdriver.lib

Interface ComboBox.Selectable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IOperable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComboBox.AbstractSelect, ComboBox.DojoSelect, ComboBox.DojoSelect_ComboBox, ComboBox.DojoSelect_FilteringSelect, ComboBox.DojoSelect_Select, ComboBox.HtmlSelect, ComboBox.SapSelect_ComboBox
    Enclosing class:
    ComboBox

    public static interface ComboBox.Selectable
extends IOperable
    This interface wraps different kinds of ComboBox, and it provides the uniform methods.
    In the class ComboBox, we call these uniform methods.

    Jan 15, 2014 (Lei Wang) Initial release.
    See Also:
    ComboBox#getSelect(WebElement)
